frames.caption: A shirtless man is running through a misty forest path at night, with a full moon illuminating the scene. The trees form a dark, towering canopy, creating a mysterious and tense atmosphere.
frames.description: The scene is set in a dark, misty forest at night. A man is running along a narrow path, with the full moon casting a bright glow behind him, adding to the eerie and suspenseful mood.

frames.caption: A werewolf-like creature with glowing yellow eyes prowls through a misty forest under a full moon. The creature's muscular form is highlighted against the eerie backdrop of tall, dark trees. The scene is shrouded in fog, adding to the mysterious and ominous atmosphere.
frames.description: The scene depicts a supernatural creature, possibly a werewolf, moving through a dark, foggy forest at night. The full moon illuminates the scene, casting a ghostly glow over the surroundings.

frames.caption: A muscular humanoid figure with a wolf's head is emerging from a dark, mystical forest. Sparks and light surround the figure, creating an intense and dramatic atmosphere.
frames.description: The scene depicts a werewolf-like creature in a forest setting, surrounded by an aura of light and energy. The environment is dark and mysterious, adding to the supernatural theme.
